title: Rep. Andy Kim Is Re-elected in a New Jersey Swing District
description: Mr. Kim, a Democrat, will return to Washington for a third term after a race that appeared to narrow in recent weeks.
dc:creator: Tracey Tully, Shlomo Schorr and Lola Fadulu

media:content.media:credit: Hannah Yoon for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: Rep. Andy Kim, a Democrat, was elected to a third term.
